261
0:10:51.26,000 --> 0:10:54,000
So we have an in-built system

262
0:10:54.26,000 --> 0:10:56,000
within our own lives

263
0:10:56.26,000 --> 0:10:59,000
that ensures some kind of continuity.

264
0:10:59.26,000 --> 0:11:02,000
I like to call it an almost infinite sameness from day to day.

265
0:11:02.26,000 --> 0:11:06,000
Because if you don't have that sameness, physiologically,

266
0:11:06.26,000 --> 0:11:08,000
