283
0:11:51.26,000 --> 0:11:53,000
And it is within that region

284
0:11:53.26,000 --> 0:11:55,000
that I'm going to highlight now

285
0:11:55.26,000 --> 0:11:58,000
that we have this housing

286
0:11:58.26,000 --> 0:12:01,000
of all the life-regulation devices

287
0:12:01.26,000 --> 0:12:03,000
of the body.

288
0:12:03.26,000 --> 0:12:06,000
This is so specific that, for example,

289
0:12:06.26,000 --> 0:12:09,000
if you look at the part that is covered in red

290
0:12:09.26,000 --> 0:12:11,000
in the upper part of the brain stem,

291
0:12:11.26,000 --> 0:12:14,000
if you damage that as a result of a stroke, for example,

292
0:12:14.26,000 --> 0:12:16,000
what you get is coma

293
0:12:16.26,000 --> 0:12:18,000
or vegetative state,

294
0:12:18.26,000 --> 0:12:2,000
which is a state, of course,

295
0:12:20.26,000 --> 0:12:22,000
