300
0:12:33.26,000 --> 0:12:36,000
and, in fact, there can be images going on,

301
0:12:36.26,000 --> 0:12:38,000
being formed in the cerebral cortex,

302
0:12:38.26,000 --> 0:12:4,000
except you don't know they're there.

303
0:12:40.26,000 --> 0:12:43,000
