0:12:52.26,000 --> 0:12:54,000
It is that specific.

308
0:12:54.26,000 --> 0:12:57,000
So in that green component of the brain stem,

309
0:12:57.26,000 --> 0:13:,000
if you damage it, and often it happens,

310
0:13:00.26,000 --> 0:13:02,000
what you get is complete paralysis,

