340
0:14:11.26,000 --> 0:14:14,000
that you generate this mapping of the body

341
0:14:14.26,000 --> 0:14:17,000
that provides the grounding for the self

342
0:14:17.26,000 --> 0:14:19,000
and that comes in the form of feelings --

