404
0:16:45.26,000 --> 0:16:47,000
imagination, creativity and language.

405
0:16:47.26,000 --> 0:16:5,000
And out of that came the instruments of culture --

406
0:16:50.26,000 --> 0:16:52,000
religions, justice,

407
0:16:52.26,000 --> 0:16:54,000
